= Magic =

This page documents all magic spells in Dragon Warrior II for the NES.

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior II introduced the first multi-character party with specialized magic users. The Prince of Cannock learns offensive and utility magic, while the Princess of Moonbrooke masters both healing and powerful attack spells.

