=== Heal ===

Basic healing spell:
* Restores 30-40 HP (random)
* Essential early game
* Both spellcasters learn at level 1
* Becomes obsolete after Healmore

=== Healmore ===

Improved healing:
* Restores 85-100 HP (random)
* Main healing spell mid-game
* Cost-effective for the effect
* Learn priority: keep Princess safe

=== Healall ===

Ultimate healing:
* Fully restores HP
* Moonbrooke exclusive
* High MP cost, use wisely
* Essential for boss fights

