=== Hurt ===

Basic attack spell:
* 8-14 damage (random)
* Low MP cost
* Princess learns early
* Good for conserving MP

=== Hurtmore ===

Stronger magic attack:
* 30-50 damage
* Cost-effective damage
* Moonbrooke exclusive
* Main spell mid-game

=== Firebal ===

Fire elemental attack:
* 20-30 fire damage
* Prince of Cannock spell
* Single target only
* Decent power for cost

=== Infernos ===

Group fire attack:
* 17-25 damage per enemy
* Hits one enemy group
* Cannock exclusive
* Good for grinding

